<p>Jump to a directory, execute a command (ls), &amp; jump back</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>(cd /tmp &amp;&amp; ls)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Count the number of files in a directory:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>cd dir; ls -1 | wc -l
</code></pre></div></div>
